import math

def minimum_taxi_arrival_time(a, b, taxis):
    min_time = float('')
    for (x_i, y_i, v_i) in taxis:
        c = abs(a - x_i)
        d = abs(b - y_i)
        dis = math.sqrt(c * c + d * d)
        time = dis / v_i
        if time < min_time:
            min_time = time
    return min_time
